{"tid":2501322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：新批BioNTech付運抵港 新包裝雖印有簡體中文 但實為德國製造","createTime":"2021-04-23T09:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:44:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"22572b1e8a826f107189ac92e7798328c17a4eaa","tid":2501322,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"最新一批復必泰疫苗付運抵港<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  復星醫藥已於今日（四月二十三日）下午將BioNTech製造並從另一德國廠房（Baxter）封裝的最新一批約580 000劑復必泰疫苗付運抵港。<br />\n<br />\n  新一批次復必泰疫苗今日抵港後，工作人員隨即按既定程序，對有關疫苗進行檢查及核對，以確保疫苗符合產品規格及相關的冷鏈運輸標準。政府亦會把疫苗存放在經驗證的超低溫冷藏櫃，按藥廠指定的溫度妥善保存。<br />\n<br />\n  這批疫苗的藥瓶標籤包含英文及簡體中文，但有關批次均由相同製造商及廠房以相同規格在德國製造及封裝。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年4月23日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間17時00分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/23/P2021042300612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202104%2F23%2FP2021042300612.htm&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=b04e66ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/23/P2021042300612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"828e297ceded1ee9367f0e35c6dd8fcfb181bee3","tid":2501322,"uid":70786,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"一路走來<br />\n堅持唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/grab.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3029c6fa818e0d3c426cada1ff484acb0bd9ac38","tid":2501322,"uid":271894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as